{"tid":1373204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家香港需要一個轉捩點","createTime":"2019-07-27T14:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T08:49:42.000Z","uid":250462,"like":101,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"c8c4a637914b3b8270ff11be717a6d64b26181f1","tid":1373204,"uid":250462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:51:39.000Z","msg":"大家有眼睇，警黑合作，狗隻以作為一個有合法武力嘅機關不停瘋狂欺負百姓。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺呢度好感謝咁多位bk，香討嘅手足出黎頂左咁多次，依然再接再厲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但諗吓，每個星期輪住俾班狗打都真係唔係路。<br />\n而家有冇一個轉捩點可以打破呢個僵局，望住手足俾人輪姦真係好心痛同無助。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無意分化，亦都清楚明白抗爭係一個長期作戰，以下希望巴絲集思廣益，有乜野可以成為改變到現況嘅轉捩點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9865825713fbb0cf3943cb2483f2335d0cd6365","tid":1373204,"uid":250462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:53:17.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"5af284d742fbd4e34b609df194c3f787c6bf6432","tid":1373204,"uid":250462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:53:27.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"16aa5535ad34ce3d1944863f42ac98df641f11eb","tid":1373204,"uid":250462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:53:47.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"b1ddfe3d761e74219b43b51b120b74bd1df25633","tid":1373204,"uid":250462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:54:00.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"381bae834d656fac34094bf956db8109951cb5c0","tid":1373204,"uid":18001,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:54:59.000Z","msg":"解決咗散水果陣前線同後邊出現斷層既問題先"},{"pid":"6e61b7e5c634bea6699f926ec0c3bba1e9331636","tid":1373204,"uid":243476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:57:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e684ec7b7f854a067d834b58b5e2fb34a9c8b349","tid":1373204,"uid":274732,"like":22,"dislike":0